title: #92Noon! 9am Hour 12/22 - Russo in for PA! Tenna/Dr.Maurice/Mayer
description: Russo opens the show chatting with Tenna about USA Hockey's withdrawal from the Olympics.  Dr. Bill Maurice calls in to discuss the Omicron variant sweeping through sports right now, and NHL executive Steve Mayer joins to talk about the NHL Winter Classic.
